 Sat Dec  8 2012 - added color.label to taskrc-gtk+
 Fri Dec  7 2012 - added <tab> completion when using 'p' to set project
 Thu Dec  6 2012 - added 'p' for setting project

 Wed Dec  5 2012 - released v0.6
